Description: # ssml-builder
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```
        pip install ssml-builder
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        1. Create a Speech object
        
        ```
        from ssml_builder.core import Speech
        speech = Speech()
        ```
        
        1. Add text and tags
        
        ```
        # add text
        speech.say("hello world")
        # add pause tag
        speech.pause("10s")
        # add prosody tag
        speech.prosody("x-fast")
        ```
        
        1. Output ssml with \<speak\> wrapper
        ```
        speech.speak()
        ```
        
